<h2><span class="mw-headline" id="MCA_Records_recording_artists">MCA Records recording artists</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=MCA_Records&amp;action=edit&amp;section=12" title="Edit section: MCA Records recording artists">edit</a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h2>
